{"title":"Ubuntu传递文件","uid":"ca6a15f1a0c973b3ab8c2d89ae7c194d","slug":"ubuntu拖拽文件","date":"2023-10-13T01:17:12.000Z","updated":"2023-11-05T07:35:35.701Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ubuntu拖拽文件.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>在安装完Ubuntu后想传输文件非常的麻烦</p>\n<p>网上查阅教程大多都说安装完VMware tools 后便可自由拖拽文件，但安装完后并不行</p>\n<p>查阅发现从Ubuntu14.04开始open-vm-tools 代替了官方 VMware Tools，所以应该改安装open-vm-tools。</p>\n<h1 id=\"步骤\"><a href=\"#步骤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"步骤\"></a>步骤</h1><p><strong>1.打开Ubuntu的设置页面，打开关于-软件更新，更改下载自：来自中国的服务器，关闭窗口，重启Ubuntu</strong></p>\n<p><strong>2.打开终端，输入sudo apt-get install open-vm-tools-desktop，根据提示完成安装后应该能观察到页面自动调整了大小，此时说明安装成功。重新启动Ubuntu便可拖拽传输文件</strong></p>\n","text":"在安装完Ubuntu后想传输文件非常的麻烦 网上查阅教程大多都说安装完VMware tools 后便可自由拖拽文件，但安装完后并不行 查阅发现从Ubuntu14...","permalink":"/post/ubuntu拖拽文件","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":302,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"教程","slug":"教程","count":2,"path":"api/categories/教程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Ubuntu","slug":"Ubuntu","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Ubuntu.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">步骤</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"SoldAllFruit","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"SZU/IC-Studying...","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/fruit-lxe","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/From_start_quit?spm=1010.2135.3001.5343","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"Risc-V Milkv-duo资料","uid":"877f93e851421056f5250da2e1f421b3","slug":"Risc-V-资料","date":"2023-10-14T02:43:55.000Z","updated":"2023-11-05T07:35:33.661Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Risc-V-资料.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/RISC-cover.jpg","text":"RISC-V官方网站：RISC主页 RISC-V官方社区：RISC-V官方社区 sdkGitHub：GitHub - milkv-duo&#x2F;duo-bu...","permalink":"/post/Risc-V-资料","ph